textDelta: With urbanization what food commodities rise? With urbanization, the price of food commodities that are in high demand, such as meat and dairy, typically rise.
What type body functions do dietary protein help with? Protein helps the body with muscle growth and maintenance, as well as with the production of enzymes and hormones.

Open door notes are what? Open door notes are a type of communication in which a sender leaves a note for a recipient who is not present. Open door notes can be used to communicate with coworkers, classmates, or family members.
Open door notes are what? What type treaty with America is an Open door note? Open door notes are notes that allow for free trade between two countries.
Is silicon an oxide? Silicon dioxide is a compound of silicon and oxygen. Silicon is not an oxide.
what type element is silicon found in? (form) silicon is found in the form of silicon dioxide, which is also known as quartz.
in what naturally occurring form is silicon found? Silicon is found in a variety of minerals, the most common of which is quartz.
